#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:2
msgid "快速开始"
msgstr "Quick Start"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:4
msgid ""
"PCBA AOI 软件是一款面向电子制造的智能光学检测系统。 系统以视觉 AI 为核心，提供从自动建模、参数生成到缺陷检测与持续优化的完整流程。 "
"与传统需要频繁手动调参的方式不同，系统可快速适配生产现场，在提升效率的同时确保精度与稳定性。 "
"依托自适应算法与反馈机制，软件既能识别常见与细微缺陷，也能在生产过程中持续学习，提升良率并降低运维成本。"
msgstr ""
"The PCBA AOI software is an Automated Optical Inspection system for "
"electronics manufacturing. Centered on vision AI, it covers the full "
"workflow from auto-programming and parameter generation to defect "
"detection and continuous improvement. Unlike conventional approaches that"
" need frequent manual tuning, the system adapts quickly to the production"
" floor and lifts efficiency without sacrificing accuracy or stability. "
"Backed by adaptive algorithms and a feedback loop, it catches both common"
" and subtle defects and keeps learning during production — raising yield "
"and reducing maintenance cost."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:9
msgid "本章节演示如何使用 AOI 系统快速完成一块 PCB 的建模、检测与反馈流程。"
msgstr ""
"This chapter walks through programming a PCB, running an inspection, and "
"submitting feedback end-to-end using the AOI system."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:12
msgid "启动软件"
msgstr "Software Launch"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:14
msgid "在开始之前，建议您进行以下设置以优化性能："
msgstr ""
"Before you start, we recommend the following settings to optimize "
"performance:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:16
msgid ":ref:`如何避免 GPU 进入低功耗模式导致推理变慢？`"
msgstr ":ref:`如何避免 GPU 进入低功耗模式导致推理变慢？`"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:17
msgid ":ref:`如何开启浏览器的硬件加速以避免浏览器卡顿？`"
msgstr ":ref:`如何开启浏览器的硬件加速以避免浏览器卡顿？`"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:19
msgid "在桌面点击启动器即可启动软件。"
msgstr "Start the software by clicking the launcher on the desktop."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "启动软件界面"
msgstr "Launcher"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:25
msgid "浏览器将自动打开 ``http://localhost:3005/``。 后端默认地址为 ``http://localhost:8000/``。"
msgstr ""
"The browser will automatically open ``http://localhost:3005/``. The "
"default backend address is ``http://localhost:8000/``."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "登录界面"
msgstr "Login page"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:32
msgid "如需更换后端地址，可在登录页点击 **Change Host Address（更改主机地址）**，在弹窗中填写后端 URL 后保存。"
msgstr ""
"To switch to a different backend, click **Change Host Address** on the "
"login page, enter the backend URL in the dialog, and save."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "更改主机地址"
msgstr "Change Host Address"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:39
msgid "如需从其他设备访问，将 ``localhost`` 替换为目标机器的 IP。"
msgstr ""
"To access from another device, replace ``localhost`` with the target "
"machine's IP address."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:43
msgid "登录与设置"
msgstr "Login and Settings"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:45
msgid "首次进入可以使用 **管理员** 账号登录：用户名 **admin**，密码在部署时提供。"
msgstr ""
"On first use, log in with the **administrator** account — username "
"**admin**; the password is provided at deployment time."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:47
msgid "登录后，点击右上角的 **齿轮图标** 进入 **设置** 页面。设置页左侧分为 **团队**、**管理模型**、**系统设置** 等分组。"
msgstr ""
"After logging in, click the **gear icon** at the top right to open "
"**Settings**. The left side of Settings is split into **Team**, **Manage "
"Models**, **System Settings**, and more."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "设置界面"
msgstr "Settings view"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:53
msgid ""
"在左侧展开 **系统设置**，选择 **语言**，即可在 **系统语言** 中切换界面语言（如 ``English`` / "
"``中文``）。语言设置会保存在系统中，并在系统重启后生效。"
msgstr ""
"Expand **System Settings** on the left and pick **Language**; use the "
"**System Language** drop-down to switch the UI language (e.g. ``English``"
" / ``中文``). The change takes effect immediately, and your choice is saved"
" and kept after a system restart."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "语言设置"
msgstr "Language setting"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:59
msgid "更多设置选项请参见 :ref:`系统管理` 章节。"
msgstr "For more configuration options, see the :ref:`系统管理` chapter."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:62
msgid "注册产品"
msgstr "Register a product"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:64
msgid ""
"在主页点击 **训练PCBA**（注册新的 PCBA/产品），进入 **自动编程向导**。向导分为 5 个步骤：**基本信息**、**将 PCB "
"放置在传送带上**、**获取尺寸**、**拍摄**、**添加 CAD（可选）**。"
msgstr ""
"From Home, click **Train PCBA** to register a new PCBA / product and open"
" the **Auto-Programming wizard**. The wizard runs through five steps: "
"**Basic Info**, **Place PCB on Conveyor**, **Get Dimensions**, "
"**Capture**, and **Add CAD (Optional)**."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "创建产品-自动编程向导"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:70
msgid "**1. 基本信息**"
msgstr "**1. Basic Info**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:72
msgid ""
"输入 **产品名称**；在 **自动编程检测类型** 中按需勾选关注的检测项（如 本体、极性、焊点、焊盘沾胶、IC 引脚、文字 "
"等）；如有需要，可在 **自动编程参数** 中开启 **桥接** 检测并设置 **邻近距离（像素）** 阈值。完成后点击 **下一步**。"
msgstr ""
"Enter the **Product Name**; check the inspection types you care about "
"under **Auto-Programming inspection types** (Body, Polarity, Solder "
"Joint, Glue on Pad, IC Lead, Text, and so on). If needed, enable "
"**Bridge** under **Auto-Programming parameters** and set the **Adjacency "
"Distance (pixels)** threshold. Click **Next**."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "创建产品-基本信息"
msgstr "Create Product — Basic Info"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:78
msgid "**2. 将 PCB 放置在传送带上**"
msgstr "**2. Place the PCB on the Conveyor**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:80
msgid ""
"选择对应传送带并点击 **锁定传送带**，确认或输入传送带宽度后点击 **进板**，PCB 将自动输送至相机下方的拍摄/定位区域；到位后点击 "
"**下一步**。"
msgstr ""
"Pick the conveyor and click **Lock Conveyor**, confirm or enter the "
"conveyor width, then click **PCB In**. The PCB is fed automatically into "
"the capture / alignment area under the camera. Once it's in position, "
"click **Next**."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
#, fuzzy
msgid "创建产品-将 PCB 放置在传送带上"
msgstr "**2. Place the PCB on the Conveyor**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:86
msgid "**3. 获取尺寸**"
msgstr "**3. Get Dimensions**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:88
msgid ""
"若已知 PCB 尺寸，直接输入其宽度与高度（单位：mm）。若尺寸不确定，可移动相机分别拍摄 PCB "
"左下角与右上角，在图像上依次点击这两个位置并选择 **自动计算**，系统将自动推算尺寸。"
msgstr ""
"If you know the PCB dimensions, type the width and height directly (in "
"mm). If not, move the camera to capture the bottom-left and top-right "
"corners of the PCB, click those two positions on the image in turn, and "
"choose **Auto-calculate**; the system infers the dimensions."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "创建产品-获取尺寸"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:94
msgid "**4. 拍摄**"
msgstr "**4. Capture**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:96
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"点击拍摄，系统将联动相机与传送带分区采集并自动拼接生成完整 PCB "
"图像；随后框选用于自动编程的有效区域（通常为整板；若需排除治具/夹具边缘，可适当收缩）。该基准图像将作为后续自动编程、对齐与检测的参考，尽量使用洁净、无缺陷的"
" **Golden board（良品板）** 拍摄。此界面可实时调整相机参数（**曝光时间**、**增益**、**gamma** "
"等）；如效果不佳，可重新拍摄覆盖上一版本。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Capture**; the system coordinates the camera and conveyor to "
"acquire the board in tiles and stitch them into a full PCB image. Then "
"box the effective area used for Auto-Programming (usually the entire "
"board; shrink it slightly to exclude any fixture / jig edges). This "
"reference image is the baseline for subsequent Auto-Programming, "
"alignment, and inspection, so it must be captured from a clean, defect-"
"free **Golden board**. Camera parameters — **Exposure**, **Gain**, "
"**gamma** — can be tuned live on this screen; if the result is poor, re-"
"capture to overwrite the previous version."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
#, fuzzy
msgid "创建产品-拍摄"
msgstr "Create Product — Basic Info"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:102
msgid "**5. 添加 CAD（可选）**"
msgstr "**5. Add CAD (Optional)**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:104
msgid ""
"提供 CAD（``.csv``）文件后，系统可自动读取封装(Package)、丝印/标识、料号(PN)、X/Y "
"坐标与旋转角度，并按封装或料号聚类，使同类元件一次建模、加速训练，同时减少后续人工分组与命名工作。"
msgstr ""
"Providing a CAD file (``.csv``) lets the system read Package, silkscreen "
"/ designator, Part Number (PN), X / Y coordinates, and rotation angle "
"automatically; cluster components by package or part number so identical "
"components are modeled once and training is faster; and cut down on later"
" manual grouping and naming work."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:106
msgid ""
"上传 ``.csv`` 文件后点击 "
"**预览表格**，在字段映射界面依次指定：料号(PN)、封装(Package)、X、Y、旋转(°)，（可选）层/板面字段；选择坐标单位（mm 或 "
"mil），确认原点与方向一致，随后点击 **运行自动编程**。若 CAD 与拍摄图像未正确重合，可在对齐界面通过旋转、平移、缩放微调后重新运行。"
msgstr ""
"Upload the ``.csv`` file and click **Preview Table**. In the field-"
"mapping screen, assign — in order — Part Number (PN), Package, X, Y, "
"Rotation (°), and (optionally) the layer / side field. Pick the "
"coordinate unit (mm or mil), confirm the origin and orientation match the"
" captured image, then click **Run Auto-Programming**. If the CAD doesn't "
"overlap the captured image correctly, use the alignment screen to rotate "
"/ translate / scale until it does, then re-run."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:108
msgid "若不提供 CAD，后续自动编程仍可执行；检测质量不受影响，仅失去基于封装/料号的聚类加速，系统将对元件逐一建模。自动编程耗时约 30 秒。"
msgstr ""
"Without CAD, Auto-Programming still runs; inspection quality is "
"unaffected — you only lose the package / part-number clustering "
"acceleration, and the system models each component one by one. Auto-"
"Programming takes about 30 seconds."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "创建产品-添加 CAD"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:115
msgid "产品编程页面"
msgstr "Product Programming Page"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:117
msgid "自动编程完成后，会进入 **产品编程页面**。顶部提供多个标签页："
msgstr ""
"When Auto-Programming finishes, the **Product Programming page** opens. "
"Several tabs sit at the top:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:119
msgid "**标记/对齐 PCB**"
msgstr "**Mark/Align PCB**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:120
msgid "**模板编辑器**"
msgstr "**Template Editor**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:121
msgid "**PCB 拼板**"
msgstr "**PCB Array**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:122
msgid "**整板检测**"
msgstr "**Whole Board Inspection**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:124
msgid "左侧还可在 **设置（Recipe）** 与 **元件（Component）** 视图之间切换。"
msgstr ""
"The left side also toggles between the **Recipe** view and the "
"**Component** view."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:126
msgid "**标记/对齐 PCB**："
msgstr "**Mark/Align PCB**:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:128
msgid ""
"点击 **+ 标记**，在 PCB 上 **对角位置** 分别框选 2 "
"个固定的参考标记点（圆形、矩形或复杂图案均可）。框选区域应略大，以保证在轻微位移情况下仍能正确定位。当前版本最多支持 2 个 mark 点。如使用"
" A/B 面双产品检测，可另外点击 **+ 独特标记** 在每个产品上标记一处差异明显的区域，便于系统自动区分 A/B 面。"
msgstr ""
"Click **+ Mark** and box **two** stable reference marks on the PCB at "
"**opposite corners** (circles, rectangles, and complex silkscreen "
"patterns all work). Box a region slightly larger than the mark itself so "
"it still resolves under a small board shift. The current release supports"
" **up to 2 Mark Points**. For A/B-side mixed-product inspection, also "
"click **+ Unique Marker** to box a clearly-distinct area on each product "
"so the system can tell A from B automatically."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "标记对齐示例"
msgstr "Mark alignment example"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:134
msgid "**模板编辑器**："
msgstr "**Template Editor**:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:136
msgid ""
"左侧显示自动编程获得的元件列表（可在 元件 / 料号 之间切换）。若上传了 "
"CAD，系统会自动显示丝印/标识并将同类元件分组。可通过搜索栏过滤存在问题的项；对于标记不正确的元件，可手动删除并重新编程。"
msgstr ""
"The left panel lists the components Auto-Programming produced (switch "
"between **Component** and **Part Number** views). When CAD was uploaded, "
"the system shows the silkscreen / designator and groups identical "
"components automatically. Filter problematic items via the search bar; "
"for components flagged incorrectly, delete them and re-program by hand."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "模板编辑器示例"
msgstr "Template Editor example"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:142
msgid "有关手动编程的详细步骤与编辑工具用法，请参见 :ref:`手动编程与编辑工具`。"
msgstr ""
"For detailed steps on manual programming and how to use the editing "
"tools, see :ref:`手动编程与编辑工具`."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:145
msgid "训练和评估"
msgstr "Training and Evaluation"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:147
msgid ""
"确认全部元件框与属性无误后，在 **元件列表** 上方点击 **训练** 按钮启动模型训练，耗时约 1 分钟；训练完成后再点击 "
"**自动生成检测参数** 按钮，系统会基于当前模板与训练结果生成一套初始检测参数。需要批量评估所有元件时，点击列表上方的 **三角形箭头** "
"即可一键评估。"
msgstr ""
"Once every component box and property is verified, click **Train** above "
"the component list to start model training — about a minute. When "
"training finishes, click **Auto-generate Inspection Parameters**; the "
"system derives an initial parameter set from the current template and the"
" training result. To evaluate every component at once, click the "
"**triangle arrow** above the list."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:149
msgid "评估完成后，元件会以颜色标记（绿：健康；红：不健康）。可按需查看不健康项并参考 :ref:`检测参数` 继续微调。"
msgstr ""
"When evaluation finishes, each component is color-coded — green for "
"healthy, red for unhealthy. Browse the unhealthy ones and fine-tune them "
"per :ref:`检测参数`."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:153
msgid "开始检测"
msgstr "Start inspection"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:155
msgid "返回主页：点击左上角 Logo 回到主页，点击 **新建检测任务**。在弹窗中完成任务配置："
msgstr ""
"Return to Home: click the logo at the top-left, then click **New "
"Inspection Task**. In the dialog, configure:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:157
msgid "**传送带**：选择传送带；"
msgstr "**Conveyor**: pick a conveyor."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:158
msgid "**选择一个 PCBA**：选择已编程的产品；"
msgstr "**Select a PCBA**: pick a programmed product."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:159
msgid "**选择任务模式**：选择任务模式（如自动连续运行任务）；"
msgstr "**Task mode**: pick a mode (e.g. Continuous automatic)."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:160
msgid "**以演示模式运行**：对同一块 PCB 自动连续运行检测，每隔约 5 秒触发一次。适合熟悉复检/反馈流程或现场演示，无需反复手动触发。"
msgstr ""
"**Run in demo mode**: runs inspection continuously on the same PCB, "
"triggering every ~5 seconds. Useful for learning the review / feedback "
"flow or demoing on-site, without repeatedly hitting trigger."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:162
msgid "完成后点击 **开始检测**。"
msgstr "Click **Start Inspection** to begin."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "新建检测任务"
msgstr "New Inspection Task"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:168
msgid "进入检测页面后："
msgstr "On the inspection page:"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:170
msgid "按空格键，或按设备上的 **进板** 实体按键：进板并立即开始检测。更多快捷键请参见 :ref:`快捷键` 章节。"
msgstr ""
"Press the spacebar or the **PCB In** hardware button to load a board and "
"start inspection immediately. See :ref:`快捷键` for the full keyboard "
"reference."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:171
msgid "右侧信息栏：实时显示产品统计（合格/不合格）、元件合格率/不良率/误报率与检测时长（可在整板/子板之间切换）。"
msgstr ""
"The right-hand panel shows live product statistics (Pass / Fail), "
"component pass / defect / false-positive rates, and inspection time — "
"switchable between Board and Sub-board scope."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "检测页面"
msgstr "Live inspection page"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:177
msgid "检测到缺陷的元件会被标记，可查看放大图、定位框、缺陷类型及判定依据，并立即反馈。反馈后的数据会写入数据集，供后续持续优化使用。"
msgstr ""
"Defective components are flagged; you can examine the zoomed image, the "
"localization box, the defect type, and the deciding feature, and submit "
"feedback immediately. Feedback flows into the dataset for ongoing "
"optimization."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "复检页面整体视图"
msgstr "Review page overall view"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:184
msgid "查看检测历史"
msgstr "Inspection history"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:186
msgid ""
"在主页点击 **工作列表** 进入 **数据分析报告**。页面包含 **总结**、**检测结果**、**不良元件**、**误判元件** "
"等标签，并可按 今天 / 昨天 / 本周 / 本月 / 今年 过滤。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Worklist** on Home to open the **Data Analysis Report**. The page"
" exposes the **Summary**, **Inspection Results**, **Defective "
"Components**, and **False-Positive Components** tabs, with time-range "
"presets — Today / Yesterday / This Week / This Month / This Year."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:188
msgid "**总结** 提供 OK/NG 数量与比例、告警/误报的 PPM、DPU 等总览指标，以及 NG/OK 比例图。"
msgstr ""
"**Summary** offers overview metrics — OK / NG counts and ratios, alerted "
"/ false-positive PPM, DPU, and an NG / OK ratio chart."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "数据分析报告-总结"
msgstr "Data Analysis Report — Summary"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:194
msgid ""
"切换到 **检测结果**，可查看每次检测记录：PCBA 名称、序列号、元件数、不良/告警元件数、检测起止时间等。点击某条记录的 **查看** "
"进入复检详情。"
msgstr ""
"Switch to **Inspection Results** to browse each inspection record: PCBA "
"name, serial number, component count, defective / alerted component "
"counts, start and end times. Click **View** on a row to enter the review "
"detail."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "检测结果列表"
msgstr "Inspection results list"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:200
msgid "在复检详情中，左侧列出不良元件，中部与右侧展示整板及缺陷的放大图、定位框、缺陷类型与判定依据，并可直接反馈。"
msgstr ""
"In the review detail, the NG components are listed on the left; the "
"whole-board view, the zoomed defect image, the localization box, the "
"defect type, and the deciding feature appear in the center and right, "
"with feedback submission inline."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
msgid "复检详情与反馈"
msgstr "Review detail and feedback"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:206
msgid "提交的反馈会写入数据集，用于后续再训练与参数自适应迭代。"
msgstr ""
"Submitted feedback flows into the dataset for retraining and adaptive "
"parameter iteration."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:210
msgid "迭代模型"
msgstr "Iterate the model"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:212
msgid "反馈写入数据集后，回到产品编程页面重新训练并评估，针对仍为红色的异常元件微调参数即可完成一次迭代。"
msgstr ""
"After feedback flows into the dataset, return to the programming page, "
"retrain and evaluate, then fine-tune the parameters for any components "
"still showing red — that completes one iteration."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:214
msgid ""
"在复检页提交反馈后，也可直接点击 **AI 更新（AI Update）** 一键据反馈更新检测参数并重训，再点 **应用参数更新（Apply "
"Param Updates）** 并重新加载会话即可生效，无需回到编程页。"
msgstr ""
"After submitting feedback on the review page, you can also click **AI "
"Update** to update parameters and retrain from that feedback in one step,"
" then click **Apply Param Updates** and reload the session to apply it — "
"no need to return to the programming page."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:219
msgid "以上即为快速开始全部流程，感谢您的使用。后续更多功能与更详细的说明请继续阅读完整用户手册。"
msgstr ""
"That's the complete Quick Start flow. Thanks for using the system — read "
"on through the full user manual for additional features and deeper "
"documentation."

